properties.name: lore
properties.value: My brothers. I must admit that I am scared. Ever since you found me on the streets, I’ve considered you a family. To think I would end up working on such an important task. ME! Once, a broken husk among vibrant, pompous people. Where are those snakes now? Dead…and rotting below. While I shall be a harbinger of the Dread Lord, but…..what shall become of me? Will I be judged by another Elder? What punishment would I pay for the crimes I committed? Would the Dread Lord save me? I can’t stop asking questions...

properties.name: lore
properties.value: and you have all given me answers, but….where does it end? When you meet him, please ask him to find me. If not, at least ask him to remember my name….remember my sacrifice, Remember my Determination, My Charisma, My Courage, My Knowledge, My Wisdom, My Strength, My Fire—My—My—MY DEVOTION! UNRELENTING! FERVENT! DEVOTION! 🜆🜎🜄🜑🜨🝗🝓🜬🜹🝐 🝜🝒🜽🜻🜴🜾🜆🜎🜄🜑🜨🝗🝓🜬🜹🝐 🝜🝒🜽🜻🜴🜾🜆🜎🜄🜑🜨🝗🝓🜬🜹🝐🝜 🝒🜽🜻🜆🜎🜄🜑🜨🝗🝓🜬🜹🝐🝜 🝒🜽🜻🜴🜾🜆🜎...
